for this project need to install all devOps tools :) 
k8s minicube helm and more and more 
if you can't please get out of here

For start backup need to run 
./startBackup.sh

For stoping backup need to run  
./stopBackup.sh

For restore
./restoreLast.sh

if you have some problem with running script please not forgotten chmod
chmod +x $script name 